   <p begin="00:11:09.878" end="00:11:10.879" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカピカ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:11.380" end="00:11:15.425" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ムサシ）あ〜ら わざわざ<br />ピカチュウのほうから来てくれたわ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:15.509" end="00:11:17.928" style="s1"><span style="s2">（シトロン）くっ…<br />（サトシ）みんなを返せ ロケット団</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:18.470" end="00:11:20.597" style="s1"><span style="s2">みんなを返せと言われたら…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:20.972" end="00:11:22.891" style="s1"><span style="s2">答えてあげるが世の情け</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:23.558" end="00:11:25.394" style="s1"><span style="s2">世界の破壊を防ぐため</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:25.894" end="00:11:28.355" style="s1"><span style="s2">世界の平和を守るため</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:28.438" end="00:11:31.525" style="s1"><span style="s2">愛と真実の悪を貫く</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:31.608" end="00:11:33.902" style="s1"><span style="s2">ラブリーチャーミーな<span style="s5"><span style="s6">敵</span><span style="s7">かたき</span></span>役</span></p> 
