   <p begin="00:13:19.049" end="00:13:20.050" style="s1"><span style="s2">リマ〜</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:22.844" end="00:13:24.429" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハリマロン！　くっ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:24.763" end="00:13:27.933" style="s1"><span style="s2">リマ リマ リマ… リマッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:28.517" end="00:13:30.602" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ハリマロン）リマ〜<br />（シトロン）うっ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:30.685" end="00:13:32.771" style="s1"><span style="s2">くうっ… うっ</span></p> 
