   <p begin="00:14:47.887" end="00:14:49.431" style="s1"><span style="s2">（シトロン）ハア ハア…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:50.599" end="00:14:51.683" style="s1"><span style="s2">これは…</span></p> 
